fabric.messages

Class MessageToWorkerHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • fabric.messages.AbstractMessageServer
      • fabric.messages.MessageToWorkerHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageHandler, java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    RemoteCallManager

    public abstract class MessageToWorkerHandler
extends AbstractMessageServer
    This abstract class acts as a visitor for MessagesToWorker. It also documents the list of all messages that a worker needs to be able to handle. The methods all have the form: 
     public Response handle(Principal, Message)
   throws FabricException
    and there is one such method for each message type that the worker handles.
